# TECH_STACK.md
## Interior Design & Renovation Cost Estimation Web App

---

## 1. Overview

This document defines the complete technology stack for the Interior Design & Renovation Cost Estimation Web Application.  
The stack is optimized for:
- Fast MVP development
- Low operational cost
- Scalability
- SEO and lead generation
- Clean admin and estimation workflows

---

## 2. Frontend Stack

### Framework
- **Next.js (React Framework)**
- **TypeScript**

### Styling & UI
- **Tailwind CSS**
- **ShadCN UI**
- **Radix UI (via ShadCN)**

### Frontend Responsibilities
- Landing pages (SEO optimized)
- Multi-step cost estimation wizard
- Package comparison UI
- Admin dashboard UI
- Responsive design (mobile-first)

---

## 3. Backend Stack

### Runtime & Framework
- **Node.js**
- **Express.js**
- **TypeScript**

### Backend Responsibilities
- Cost calculation engine
- Package & pricing management
- Furniture & renovation logic
- Lead management
- PDF quotation generation
- Authentication & authorization

