## 4. Database Layer

### Database
- **PostgreSQL**

### ORM
- **Prisma ORM**

### Data Managed
- Packages (Basic / Standard / Premium)
- Pricing rules (per sq. ft)
- Furniture catalog
- Renovation options
- Location multipliers
- Users & roles
- Generated estimates
- Leads

---

## 5. Authentication & Authorization

- **NextAuth.js**
- Email / Google authentication
- Role-based access:
  - Admin
  - Sales
  - Viewer (optional)

---

## 6. Cost Estimation Engine

### Type
- Rule-based pricing engine

### Logic
Base Cost = Area (sq.ft) × Package Rate
Total Cost = Base Cost
+ Furniture Cost
+ Renovation Add-ons
× Location Multiplier


### Characteristics
- Configurable via admin panel
- City-based price adjustment
- Package-based rules

